<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="emerald">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Poppins:wght@100;400;500;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">

    <!-- Stylesheets-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="output.css">
    <title>Counting Cows</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="drawer">
        <input id="my-drawer" type="checkbox" class="drawer-toggle" />
        <div class="drawer-content flex flex-col">
            <!-- Navbar -->
            <header class="navbar bg-neutral text-neutral-content">
                <div class="navbar-start">
                    <label for="my-drawer" class="btn btn-square btn-ghost">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                                d="M10 3a1 1 0 011 1v5h5a1 1 0 110 2h-5v5a1 1 0 11-2 0v-5H4a1 1 0 110-2h5V4a1 1 0 011-1z"
                                clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                        <!-- <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            class="inline-block w-6 h-6 stroke-current">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
                        </svg> -->
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="navbar-center">
                    <h1 class=" text-center text-2xl font-bold">Counting Cows</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="navbar-end">
                    <!-- The button to open modal -->
                    <label for="my-modal-3" class="btn modal-button btn-info">Rules</label>

                    <input type="checkbox" id="my-modal-3" class="modal-toggle" />
                    <div class="modal">
                        <div class="modal-box relative prose">
                            <label for="my-modal-3" class="btn btn-sm btn-circle absolute right-2 top-2">✕</label>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-center mb-5">Counting Cows Rulebook</h3>
                            <h4>Overview</h4>
                            <p>You are trying to become a successful farmer by collecting various forms of livestock.
                                The player with the most livestock wins.</p>
                            <h4>Getting Livestock</h4>
                            <p>You can play with any available living creatures (cows, sheep, goats, horses, dogs, cats,
                                frogs, llamas, whatever) or you can restrict the game to certain species.</p>
                            <p>To claim animals, you estimate their number and say, “I claim [12] cows!”. Whoever speaks
                                first claims the animals, adding them to their personal livestock tallies.</p>
                            <p>Other players can contest the claim by counting the animals and reporting the actual
                                number, “Actually, there are [15] cows!”. If the first player estimated incorrectly,
                                they get no new animals and the player contesting the claim gets to keep all the animals
                                instead.</p>
                            <h4>Marry Your Animals</h4>
                            <p>If you pass a church/synagogue/municipal office or other location associated with
                                marriage ceremonies, a player may say “I marry my [cows]!”. When you marry your [cows],
                                they reproduce, doubling their number. Each church may only be used once: one church,
                                one
                                player, one species married. Interspecies marriage is forbidden in this game.</p>
                            <h4>Kill Your Opponent's Animals</h4>
                            <p>If you pass a graveyard, cemetary, or other silimar location, a player may say "I kill
                                [Jeremy's]
                                cows!" You must specify who's animals you are killing. That species of animal is reduced
                                to zero.</p>
                            <h4>Store Animals in a Barn</h4>
                            <p>To protect against loss, you can stash your animals safely inside any barn that you pass
                                by saying “I put my [cows] into that barn!”. One barn, one player, one species
                                protected. Once inside the barn, animals cannot be killed or married.</p>
                            <h4>Ending the Game</h4>
                            <p>The game ends when you reach your destination or the players get tired of the game. If
                                you're playing with multiple species, you may assign different point values to each
                                species. The person with the biggest farm wins!</p>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </header>

            <!-- Page content -->
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">

                <div class="flex flex-col m-3 items-center gap-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-serif">Select a Farm:</h2>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-3">
                        <% for(let i=0; i < players.length; i++) {%>
                            <div class="btn btn-primary w-56">
                                <input id="radioPlayer<%= i %>" type="radio" name="radioPlayer"
                                    class="radio radio-secondary mr-3" value="<%= players[i].playerName %>" />
                                <label for="radioPlayer<%= i %>" class="label cursor-pointer custom-button">
                                    <%= players[i].farmName %>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-serif">Select an Animal:</h2>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
                        <div class="btn btn-primary w-32 min-w-fit">
                            <label class="label cursor-pointer custom-button">
                                <input type="radio" name="radioAnimal" class="radio radio-secondary mr-3"
                                    value="Cows" />
                                Cows
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-primary w-32 min-w-fit">
                            <label class="label cursor-pointer custom-button">
                                <input type="radio" name="radioAnimal" class="radio radio-secondary mr-3"
                                    value="Sheep" />
                                Sheep
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-primary w-32 min-w-fit">
                            <label class="label cursor-pointer custom-button">
                                <input type="radio" name="radioAnimal" class="radio radio-secondary mr-3"
                                    value="Horses" />
                                Horses
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-primary w-32 min-w-fit">
                            <label class="label cursor-pointer custom-button">
                                <input type="radio" name="radioAnimal" class="radio radio-secondary mr-3"
                                    value="Goats" />
                                Goats
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-primary w-32 min-w-fit">
                            <label class="label cursor-pointer custom-button">
                                <input type="radio" name="radioAnimal" class="radio radio-secondary mr-3"
                                    value="Other" />
                                Other
                            </label>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-5 mt-5">
                        <div class="flex gap-3">
                            <label class="label" for="number">
                                <span class="label-text text-xl font-serif">Number:</span>
                            </label>
                            <input type="number" class="input input-bordered w-20" id="number" name="number">
                            <button id="byNumber" class="btn btn-secondary w-28 custom-button">Submit</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="divider text-secondary font-bold font-serif">OR</div>
                        <div class="flex gap-2 m-2">
                            <button id="barn" class="btn btn-secondary w-24 custom-button">Barn</button>
                            <button id="marry" class="btn btn-secondary w-24 custom-button">Marry</button>
                            <button id="kill" class="btn btn-secondary w-24 custom-button">Kill</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-neutral py-3 w-full rounded-box">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-normal text-neutral-content font-serif py-2">Rankings:</h2>
                        <div class="bg-white h-0.5 w-3/4 rounded mb-3"></div>
                        <% for(let i=0; i < players.length; i++) {%>
                            <div class="text-center py-2">
                                <h3 class="text-accent text-xl font-normal font-serif">
                                    <%= players[i].farmName %>
                                </h3>
                                <span class="text-neutral-content">
                                    Livestock : <%= players[i].farmTotal %>
                                </span>
                            </div>

                            <% } %>
                    </div>

                    <ul class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                        <!-- Player Card -->
                        <% for(let i=0; i < players.length; i++) {%>
                            <div class="flex flex-col my-2 p-4 border border-primary rounded-box">
                                <!-- Don't change these-->
                                <h3 class="text-xl text-center font-serif">
                                    <%= players[i].farmName %>
                                </h3>
                                <h4 class="text-center">
                                    <%= players[i].playerName %>
                                </h4>
                                <!-- End Don't Change these-->
                                <div class="flex mt-3">
                                    <ul class="w-1/2">
                                        <li> Grazing Count:
                                            <%= players[i].grazingCount %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Cows:
                                            <%= players[i].farmCows %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Sheep:
                                            <%= players[i].farmSheep %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Horses:
                                            <%= players[i].farmHorses %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Goats:
                                            <%= players[i].farmGoats %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Other:
                                            <%= players[i].farmOther %>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ul class="w-1/2">
                                        <li> Barn Count:
                                            <%= players[i].barnCount %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Cows:
                                            <%= players[i].barnCows %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Sheep:
                                            <%= players[i].barnSheep %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Horses:
                                            <%= players[i].barnHorses %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Goats:
                                            <%= players[i].barnGoats %>
                                        </li>
                                        <li> Other:
                                            <%= players[i].barnOther %>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>

                                <div class="self-end trash cursor-pointer"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                        class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"
                                        stroke-width="2">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                            d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16" />
                                    </svg></div>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="drawer-side">
            <label for="my-drawer" class="drawer-overlay"></label>
            <div class="menu p-5 overflow-y-auto w-72 bg-base-100 flex flex-col items-center">
                <!-- Sidebar content here -->
                <!-- <div class="px-2 mx-2">
                    <button id="rules" class="btn btn-info text-xl">Rules</button>
                </div> -->

                <div class="divider"></div>
                <!--New Player-->
                <form action="/addPlayer" method="POST" class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="form-control w-full max-w-xs  text-center">
                        <label class="label" for="playerName">
                            <span class="label-text text-xl font-serif">Player's Name:</span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Type here" class="input input-bordered w-full max-w-xs"
                            id="playerName" name="playerName" />
                        <label class="label" for="farmName">
                            <span class="label-text text-xl font-serif">Farm Name:</span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Type here" class="input input-bordered w-full max-w-xs"
                            id="farmName" name="farmName" />

                        <input class="btn btn-primary mt-3" type="submit" value="Create New Player">
                    </div>
                </form><!-- New Player -->
                <!-- <button class="btn btn-warning">Reset All Players</button> -->

            </div>
        </div>

        <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>